```

### Sign In

Authenticate existing users:

```typescript
const response = await guardian.signin({
  username: 'user@example.com',
  password: 'SecurePass123!',
  metaInfo: {
    ip: '192.168.1.1',
    deviceName: 'iPhone 12'
  }
